remarks.format: ## Remarks 將 XAML 命名空間前置詞對應至完整的 XAML 命名空間 URI。 maps XAML namespace prefixes to the complete XAML namespace URI. XAML 應用程式中的使用方式和一般的 XAML 命名空間，URI 通常不是結構描述樣式的 URI，其中包含`http://`。For XAML usage in applications and XAML namespaces in general, the URI is often not a schema-style URI that includes `http://`. 它是改為使用者定義對應到 CLR 命名空間和組件。It is instead a user-defined mapping to a CLR namespace and assembly. 組件包含支援型別所參考。That assembly contains the backing types being referred to. 如需詳細資訊，請參閱 < [XAML 命名空間和命名空間對應 WPF XAML](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/xaml-namespaces-and-namespace-mapping-for-wpf-xaml.md)。For details, see [XAML Namespaces and Namespace Mapping for WPF XAML](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/xaml-namespaces-and-namespace-mapping-for-wpf-xaml.md). 加入 XAML 命名空間範圍的概念。The adds the concept of scope for a XAML namespace. 預設值可能包含前置詞的索引鍵和 XML 命名空間 URI 值。A default might contain prefix keys and XML namespace URI values. 中的範圍概念平行 XML 概念可能會重新定義前置詞。The scope concept in parallels the XML concept that a prefix might be redefined. 如果是的話，重新定義僅適用於該層級或以下版本 （先前的定義適用於在 DOM 中的高層級） 的 xml DOM 檢視中。If so, the redefinition only applies at that level or below in a DOM view of the XML (the previous definition applies at higher level in the DOM). 中大部分抽範圍概念離API，例如，您可以呼叫 Api 例如而不用擔心範圍。The scope concept is mostly abstracted away in the API, such that you can call APIs such as without being concerned about scope. 不過，會公開並讓自訂變更範圍的實作可以同步處理的範圍與。However, does expose and so that a custom implementation that changes scope can synchronize with the scope for the .
